 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">36</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":36,\"repo\":\"lukassnoek/VoxelViz\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></li>","updatedAt":"2018-01-20T14:44:01.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>App Examples</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://squid-syracuse.herokuapp.com/\">Street Quality IDentification [SQUID]</a> - Highlights poor quality roads with maps, data table and photos of the offending piece of road. <a href=\"https://github.com/amyoshino/SQUID-Syracuse-Dashboard\">Source Code.</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/amyoshino/SQUID-Syracuse-Dashboard\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">18</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":18,\"repo\":\"amyoshino/SQUID-Syracuse-Dashboard\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></li>","updatedAt":"2018-01-19T17:01:25.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@plotlygraphs/introducing-dash-5ecf7191b503\">Introducing Plotly Dash</a> - A high level introduction to Dash by Chris Parmer, the author of Dash. This essay was released as part of Dash's official launch (June 21, 2017).</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-24T21:11:50.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.giacomodebidda.com/visualize-earthquakes-with-plotly-dash/\">Visualize Earthquakes with Plotly Dash</a> - Environmental scan of alternatives to Dash followed with a tutorial.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-23T21:59:22.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://alysivji.github.io/reactive-dashboards-with-dash.html\">Interactive Web-Based Dashboards in Python</a> - How the MVC model pertains to Dash and a walkthrough of building an app.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-23T09:28:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://radumas.info/blog/tutorial/2017/08/10/codeday.html\">OPS CodeDay: Dash Plotly Map + Graph</a> - How to use Jupyter notebooks in tandom with Dash to create mapping viz.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-23T09:28:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://pbpython.com/plotly-dash-intro.html\">Creating Interactive Visualizations with Plotly’s Dash Framework</a> - High level overview of how to get started with Dash.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-23T09:28:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://timothyrenner.github.io/datascience/2017/08/08/finding-bigfoot-with-dash-part-1.html\">Finding Bigfoot with Dash, Part 1</a> - Walkthrough of building a dashboard of Bigfoot sightings. <a href=\"https://timothyrenner.github.io/datascience/2017/08/09/finding-bigfoot-with-dash-part-2.html\">Part 2</a>, <a href=\"https://timothyrenner.github.io/datascience/2017/08/10/finding-bigfoot-with-dash-part-3.html\">Part 3</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-23T09:28:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>App Examples</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://bigfoot-sightings-dash.herokuapp.com/\">Finding Bigfoot</a> - Several plots (including a map), a grid layout built with Bootstrap, interactions with an input field, and caching (See also <a href=\"#tutorials\">Tutorials</a>). <a href=\"https://github.com/timothyrenner/bigfoot-dash-app\">Source Code.</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/timothyrenner/bigfoot-dash-app\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">23</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":23,\"repo\":\"timothyrenner/bigfoot-dash-app\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-17T15:11:02.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>App Examples</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://plot.ly/dash/gallery/yield-curve/\">3D Yield Curve</a> - Adapted from NYTimes's excellent <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/03/19/upshot/3d-yield-curve-economic-growth.html\">A 3-D View of a Chart That Predicts The Economic Future: The Yield Curve</a>. <a href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash-yield-curve\">Source Code.</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash-yield-curve\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">35</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":35,\"repo\":\"plotly/dash-yield-curve\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-08T14:57:30.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>App Examples</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://plot.ly/dash/gallery/recession-report/\">Recession in 255 Charts</a> - Adapted from NYTimes's excellent <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2014/06/05/upshot/how-the-recession-reshaped-the-economy-in-255-charts.html\">How the Recession Reshaped the Economy in 255 Charts</a>. <a href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash-recession-report-demo\">Source Code.</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash-recession-report-demo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">15</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":15,\"repo\":\"plotly/dash-recession-report-demo\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-08T14:55:18.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>App Examples</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://plot.ly/dash/gallery/drug-explorer/\">Drug Discovery</a> - Displays a description of the drug as you hover over points in the graph. <a href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash-drug-discovery-demo/\">Source Code.</a></li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-08T13:35:37.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>App Examples</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://plot.ly/dash/gallery/volatility-surface\">Volatility Surface Explorer</a> - Fetches CBOE options chain data from Yahoo Finance with Pandas Datareader and calculates the implied volatility of each option visualised in a 3D mesh chart. <a href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash-volatility-surface\">Source Code.</a><a data-role=\"trackaweso